{
  "stem": "19518.1",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They took them as hostages, because they gave us an ultimatum.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Cracow was, is built in a, in a circle, like, like a shoe, horseshoe.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "It's a very beautiful city, but it's surrounded also with a, with a lot of greenery.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "The old city has one layer.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "The outer city has another layer of parks.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Instead of walking through streets, you can walk through the parks and wind up in the same place, instead of walking through the crowds.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And all these areas had the-- had the Polish army was making dugouts in these areas.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And the edict was given that the Jews have to come out en masse and close up those dugouts, the, the trenches.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And they gave, I don't recall exactly, how much time to do it, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I went.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I, I never had a shovel, never mind a heavy one.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I never had one in my hand.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "But I worked one day.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "We didn't finish.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We worked another day.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Then Yom Kippur came around.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the, the Jewish police knocked on the door, would you mind?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Come, people, come out, let's go.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So I volunteered my services.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "As I said, I grew up very quickly.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the whole day on Yom Kippur, we stood there, and we were closing up whatever it was.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And the Polish people came out with water and with such venom.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Only Hitler could help [? your-- ?] you lousy Jews.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "You want water?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Here, spilt on us.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Those are the nice times in my life.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We're going to stop for a moment to change the tape.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
